title: NFL Week 1 sleeper picks, 2018 season predictions (Football 09/05)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner-McGough to break down the latest news and notes around the NFL. The guys then dive into the full CBS crew 2018 NFL season predictions before revealing some sleepers for DFS Week 1 that could make sense as smart plays.
